                "invention-title": [
                    "Acidic platinum plating solution and preparation method thereof",
                    "一种酸性镀铂溶液及其制备方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention provides an acidic platinum plating solution and a preparation method thereof, and the preparation method comprises the following steps: adding a P salt, sulfamic acid and ultrapure water for complexing at a predefined temperature; magnetons are added in the complexing process of the P salt, the sulfamic acid and the ultrapure water; after complexing of the P salt and sulfamic acid is completed, conducting salt, a brightening agent, a first reducing agent and a pre-selected additive are added; after the conducting salt, the brightener, the reducing agent, the pre-selected additive and the solution obtained by complexing the P salt and the sulfamic acid are mixed, a plating solution is obtained; transferring into an electroplating bath for electroplating; and after the plating solution is used for electroplating, a second reducing agent and P salt are regularly added for maintenance. According to the technical content disclosed by the invention, the obtained plating solution has relatively good dispersing capacity and deep plating capacity, the plating solution performance is excellent, and the cathode current efficiency is high. A plating layer with low porosity and high brightness can be obtained under the acidic plating solution."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明提供一种酸性镀铂溶液及其制备方法，包括：在预定义温度下，加入P盐、氨基磺酸及超纯水进行络合；P盐、氨基磺酸及超纯水进行络合的过程中加入磁子；P盐与氨基磺酸络合完成后，加入导电盐、光亮剂、第一还原剂及预选择的添加剂；所述导电盐、光亮剂、还原剂及预选择的添加剂和P盐与氨基磺酸络合完成的溶液混合完成后，得到镀液；转入电镀槽用于电镀；镀液用于电镀后，定期加入第二还原剂和P盐进行维护。本发明公开的技术内容，获得的镀液具有较好的分散能力和深镀能力，镀液性能优异，阴极电流效率高。在本酸性镀液下可获得低孔隙率、高光亮度的镀层。"
                }
            ]
